ission</h3><p>Take unlimited appointments without paying a fee on every booking.</p></div>\n<div class=\"card\"><h3>Set up for you</h3><p>We tailor your services, questions and hours and launch it ready to go.</p></div>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "668ceb2", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "width": {"unit": "%", "size": 100, "sizes": []}, "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "margin": {"unit": "px", "top": "0", "right": "0", "bottom": "0", "left": "0", "isLinked": true}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "flex_direction": "column"}, "elements": [{"id": "7f14b1a", "elType": "widget", "widgetType": "html", "settings": {"html": "<section>\n<div class=\"container center section-head\">\n<span class=\"eyebrow\">Your Brand, Front and Centre</span>\n<h2>Unmistakably your Manchester boutique</h2>\n<span class=\"gold-rule\"></span>\n<p class=\"lead\">Every detail is branded to you \u2014 your logo, your colours, your photography \u2014 so the booking page feels like part of your own website, not a generic form.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container grid grid-3\">\n<div class=\"card\"><svg class=\"ic\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M12 3l9 9-9 9-9-9z\"></path><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"2.4\"></circle></svg><h3>Your logo &amp; colours</h3><p>We style the whole booking journey in your boutique's colours and drop in your logo, so it looks like a natural part of your own website.</p></div>\n<div class=\"card\"><svg class=\"ic\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" viewbox=\"0 0 24 24\"><rect height=\"14\" rx=\"1.5\" width=\"18\" x=\"3\" y=\"4\"></rect><path d=\"M3 15l4-4 3 3 4-5 7 7\"></path><circle cx=\"8.5\" cy=\"8.5\" r=\"1.4\"></circle></svg><h3>Your photography</h3><p>Your own images set the tone on the booking page, f